src:
Newkidd reveals teaser images for Woochul and Yumin ahead of 'COME' release
07 Nov 2019, 19:53 by sl278



Rookie group Newkidd is preparing for a comeback with their release 'Come' and it seems like Woochul and Yumin are the first members to reveal their teaser images.
Both members show off their visuals in white shirts and silver chain necklaces. The boys definitely have a delicate, flower-boy going on, piquing more interest from fans. 
Check out the rest of the images below!
